      "path": "audio/narrations/rotation3d/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.61,
      "size": 25776,
      "text": "在平面上转动一个图形，我们只需要一个角度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotation3d",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rotation3d/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.23,
      "size": 35712,
      "text": "可到了三维空间，物体能上下俯仰、左右偏转、还能翻滚。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotation3d",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rotation3d/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.78,
      "size": 28512,
      "text": "要精确描述这种旋转，就得请出三维旋转矩阵。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotation3d",
      "section_id": "axis",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "axis-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rotation3d/xiaoxiao/axis-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.56,
      "size": 24912,
      "text": "最基本的旋转，是绕着某一根坐标轴转动。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotation3d",
      "section_id": "axis",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "axis-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rotation3d/xiaoxiao/axis-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.7,
      "size": 43200,
      "text": "绕 X 轴、绕 Y 轴、绕 Z 轴，各有一个三阶矩阵，只由正弦和余弦拼成。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotation3d",
      "section_id": "axis",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "axis-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rotation3d/xiaoxiao/axis-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.7,
      "size": 27216,
      "text": "用它去乘一个点的坐标，就得到旋转后的新位置。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotation3d",
      "section_id": "euler",
      "line_id": "eul-1",
      "filename": "euler-eul-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rotation3d/xiaoxiao/euler-eul-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.92,
      "size": 30672,
      "text": "把三个基本旋转依次相乘，就能拼出任意方向的旋转。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotation3d",
      "section_id": "euler",
      "line_id": "eul-2",
      "filename": "euler-eul-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rotation3d/xiaoxiao/euler-eul-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.12,
      "size": 17856,
      "text": "这三个角，就叫做欧拉角。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotation3d",
      "section_id": "euler",
      "line_id": "eul-3",
      "filename": "euler-eul-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rotation3d/xiaoxiao/euler-eul-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.63,
      "size": 42048,
      "text": "要注意，乘的顺序不能随便换，先转 X 再转 Y，和反过来结果不同。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotation3d",
      "section_id": "gimbal",
      "line_id": "gim-1",
      "filename": "gimbal-gim-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rotation3d/xiaoxiao/gimbal-gim-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.24,
      "size": 35856,
      "text": "当中间那个角恰好转到九十度，两根旋转轴会重叠在一起。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotation3d",
      "section_id": "gimbal",
      "line_id": "gim-2",
      "filename": "gimbal-gim-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rotation3d/xiaoxiao/gimbal-gim-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "此时系统丢失了一个自由度，这就是著名的万向锁。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotation3d",
      "section_id": "gimbal",
      "line_id": "gim-3",
      "filename": "gimbal-gim-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rotation3d/xiaoxiao/gimbal-gim-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.47,
      "size": 23472,
      "text": "工程上常改用四元数来绕开这个麻烦。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotation3d",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rotation3d/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.01,
      "size": 32112,
      "text": "拖动三个滑块，分别调整绕 X、Y、Z 轴的角度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotation3d",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rotation3d/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.63,
      "size": 26064,
      "text": "看这个立方体如何在空间里自由翻转起来。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotation3d",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rotation3d/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.7,
      "size": 27216,
      "text": "三个绕轴矩阵，是描述空间旋转的基本砖块。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotation3d",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rotation3d/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.58,
      "size": 25344,
      "text": "把它们按欧拉角相乘，就能表达任意朝向。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotation3d",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
